com.esri.mo2.src.sys
Class Properties

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.src.sys.Properties
public class Properties
extends Object

This class provides a defined ordering to the keys of a HashMap. You can put keys and their values into a Properties object, much the same as for HashMap. However, the keyIterator method will produce all keys in the order that they were added to this Properties.

This class uses an underlying ArrayList for the key ordering and a HashMap for the key-value pairs. None of the operations are synchronized, you must arrange to do this yourself.
